Package: python3-qutepart
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, ${python3:Depends}, python3-pyqt5, libpcre3
Description: Code editor component
 Some of the features:
  * Syntax highlighting for 196 languages
  * Smart indentation for many languages
  * Line numbers
  * Bookmarks
  * Advanced edit operations
  * Matching braces highlighting
  * Autocompletion based on document content
  * Vim mode
